<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Careers - Terms and Conditions</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <style>
        .terms-container {
            display: flex;
            height: 100vh;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background: url('/images/backgroundemployee.jpg') no-repeat center center;
            background-size: cover;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .terms-content {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            width: 450px;
            text-align: left;
            max-height: 80vh;
            overflow-y: auto;
        }

        .terms-content h1 {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .terms-content p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .terms-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #0078FF;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .terms-btn:hover {
            background-color: #005ecb;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="terms-container">
        <div class="terms-content">
            <h1>Terms and Conditions</h1>
            <p>1. <strong>Employment Terms:</strong> The company reserves the right to terminate employment at any time without notice. Employees must submit a termination notice both offline and online.</p>
            <p>2. <strong>Compensation:</strong> There is no compensation policy provided by the company.</p>
            <p>3. <strong>Safety Responsibility:</strong> Employee safety is the employee's own responsibility.</p>
            <p>4. <strong>Internships & Seminars:</strong> We offer business motivation programs and offline classes under our internship section.</p>
            <p>5. <strong>Document Submission:</strong> After one month of joining, employees must submit their documents for verification within a 3-month period.</p>
            
            <p>6. <strong>Mandatory Fields in Application Form:</strong> Employees must fill out the following details to submit the form:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Business Name (Required for Business Registration)</li>
                <li>Party Name (Required for all applicants)</li>
                <li>Business Location (Required for Business Registration)</li>
                <li>Business Type (Required for Business Registration)</li>
                <li>Contact Number (Required)</li>
                <li>Email ID (Required)</li>
                <li>Images Upload (Up to 20 images for business showcase)</li>
                <li>Videos Upload (Up to 10 videos for business showcase)</li>
                <li>Resume (Optional, .pdf format preferred)</li>
            </ul>

            <!-- Redirects to Career Opportunities Page -->
            <a href="/careers" class="terms-btn">Proceed accepting the Terms and Conditions</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
